{"tid":546118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉殺妻兒　韓商疑稱「結束一切」","createTime":"2018-01-31T08:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T08:15:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6bbf7eb29c097cae936836c6379e989f6cfd3c2","tid":546118,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180131/20290914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F20290914&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=a3428f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F20290914&h=eea0154c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180131/20290914</a><br />\n<br />\n涉殺妻兒　韓商疑稱「結束一切」<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180131/large/18530056.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180131%2Flarge%2F18530056.jpg&h=96eee0c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓籍商人涉殺妻兒案的精神報告顯示被告適合答辯。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】韓籍商人涉於油麻地環球貿易中心的麗思卡爾頓酒店割喉殺害42歲妻子及6歲稚子。案件昨再提堂，控方稱需進一步調查，包括取得被告保險資料及酒店閉路電視片段。控方會嘗試聯絡被告朋友，他在案發數小時前收到疑是被告來電，有人揚言要「結束一切」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方指兩份精神報告顯示被告KIM Minho（42歲）適合答辯，但警方仍需取得被告於韓國的醫療紀錄、背景資料及是否有案底，另需時間預備毒理及DNA報告。裁判官將案押後至3月27日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC175/18<br />\n■記者陸羽平、歐陽聯發"}]}